OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FKathy Wardle reports on the
OL,7,Fconnectivity issues faced by rural
OL,8,Fcommunities after Storm Goretti
OL,10,FThree months on from a storm which
OL,11,Fcaused extensive damage to Cornwall
OL,12,Fand the Isles of Scilly, questions are
OL,13,Fbeing asked about how the region could
OL,14,Fbe better prepared for future winter
OL,15,Fstorms.
OL,17,FTens of thousands of properties lost
OL,18,Fpower during the height of Storm
OL,19,FGoretti and 15,000 were without water
OL,20,Fin west Cornwall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
