OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FThe storm tore up trees and left a
OL,7,Ftrail of destruction, but it also
OL,8,Femphasised an issue which already
OL,9,Fexists in remote communities: a lack
OL,10,Fof rural connectivity.
OL,12,FHelford, in Cornwall, was one of those
OL,13,Frural areas that found itself cut off
OL,14,Fby the storm. After Goretti hit, the
OL,15,Fvillage struggled to make contact with
OL,16,Fthe outside world after the internet
OL,17,Fwent down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FThe village suffers from poor mobile
OL,7,Fphone signal, so it is one of the few
OL,8,Fareas that has been able to keep its
OL,9,Ficonic red telephone box.
OL,11,FThe phone box proved a lifeline for
OL,12,Fvillagers after the storm hit - with
OL,13,Fone describing it as a 'godsend.'
OL,15,F'People would come down here and make
OL,16,Ftheir phone calls, report faults, talk
OL,17,Fto family,' said villager John Steed
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, John Steed said:
OL,7,F"We got to keep it because an Ofcom
OL,8,Frule that says you have to have
OL,9,Fadequate mobile phone communications
OL,10,Fin the village in order for them to
OL,11,Ftake the phone box away.
OL,13,F"We have very poor mobile phone
OL,14,Fcommunication, sometimes only one bar,
OL,15,Fand we don't have data, so we got to
OL,16,Fkeep our phone box and in the end it
OL,17,Fwas a godsend."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FJohn added: "This was the only
OL,7,Fcommunication that was working in the
OL,8,Fvillage, so people would come down
OL,9,Fhere here and make their phone calls,
OL,10,Freport faults, talk to family."
OL,12,FThe old-fashioned wired phone box beat
OL,13,Fmodern mobile communications, proving
OL,14,Fvital for villagers.
OL,16,FBut, just as phone boxes have gone out
OL,17,Fof fashion, as has carrying cash and
OL,18,Fcoins. A problem that villagers then
OL,19,Ffaced once they'd begun using the
OL,20,Fphone box more frequently.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FJohn said: "The only problem was you
OL,7,Fhad to have a bag full of coins. But
OL,8,Fmost of us didn't have coins...but
OL,9,Feventually we got round that and the
OL,10,Fphone box was used quite a lot."
OL,12,FBy 2027, the UK's entire old copper
OL,13,Fwire landline network will have
OL,14,Fswitched over to a more modern digital
OL,15,Fservice, where your landline connects
OL,16,Fto a broadband router.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FBut if you have switched over, and
OL,7,Fhappen to lose power because of a
OL,8,Fstorm like Goretti, you can't use your
OL,9,Flandline - like the villagers of
OL,10,FHelford.
OL,12,FVicky Carpenter, co-founder of
OL,13,Faccessibility organisation Access
OL,14,FCornwall, said the storm caused safety
OL,15,Fissues for vulnerable people in rural
OL,16,Fareas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FVicky said: "People have been in
OL,7,Freally difficult situations, one lady
OL,8,Fcontacted me and said that her husband
OL,9,Fwas in a power chair and the battery
OL,10,Frun out and they literally couldn't
OL,11,Fmove him out of his chair for the
OL,12,Fentire time until the power came back
OL,13,Fon, which was days."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FShe added: "It all boiled down to one
OL,7,Fsimple fact, if we had our old system,
OL,8,Fwe would have been able to phone up,
OL,9,Fbut because we've transferred from
OL,10,Fanalogue phones to smart phones,
OL,11,Fthere's no signal here and people were
OL,12,Freally in quite a dangerous situation,
OL,13,Fif they were particularly vulnerable."
OL,15,FIn response, BT Openreach said the UK-
OL,16,Fwide switchover from analog to digital
OL,17,Fis critical as the old technology
OL,18,Fbecomes more unreliable. It said it
OL,19,Fdoes offer backup battery units and
OL,20,Fhybrid phones to customers with
OL,21,Fadditional needs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776438666
OL,3,CHow a telephone box became a lifeline
OL,4,Cfor village cut off by Storm Goretti
OL,6,FVirgin Media also told ITV News it has
OL,7,Fcomprehensive support measures in
OL,8,Fplace, including emergency backup
OL,9,Flines, with eight hours of battery
OL,10,Flife for customers who need them.
OL,12,FIf you do have worries about
OL,13,Fconnectivity during storms and extreme
OL,14,Fweather, it's best to contact your
OL,15,Flandline provider.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
